It is also likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on micro aerial vehicles (MAVs) and their tasks. Additionally, it may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a deep neural network for semantic segmentation. It may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories as it involves developing an algorithm for a specific task using machine learning techniques.
